    "title": "Walk-in Drive Software Engineer at Adobe India",
    "description": "Adobe India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Software Engineer for our Vijayawada operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Adobe India:\nAdobe India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Adobe India!",
